</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="298" pageNumber="299" type="note">
<paragraph pageId="298" pageNumber="299">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="298" pageNumber="299">
This taxon has been treated as a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Putzeys" authorityYear="1867" class="Hexapoda" family="Carabidae" genus="Dyschirius" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="298" pageNumber="299" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="melancholicus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="298" pageNumber="299">Dyschirius melancholicus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Putzeys by Fedorenko (1996: 149) but retained as a distinct species by Bousquet (1987a: 116) and Balkenohl and Lompe (2003: 99).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
